query:
SELECT b.id, b.siteId, b.status, b.startDate, b.endDate, b.ownerAmount, s.siteNumber, sc.name as centreName
FROM bookings b
LEFT JOIN sites s ON b.siteId = s.id
LEFT JOIN shopping_centres sc ON s.centreId = sc.id
WHERE b.status = 'confirmed' AND b.startDate >= '2026-01-01' AND b.startDate <= '2026-01-31'
LIMIT 10
